    <p>MS implemented the time course data analysis functionality for Arena3D and applied it to biological data. GAP was the first developer of the software and he contributed to the design and the implementation of the software. JA helped in analyzing and addressing specific visual concepts implemented by MS and GAP. RS conceived the concept and the main idea of Arena3D. He designed, coordinated and supervised the project. All authors drafted, read and approved the final manuscript.</p>
  </sec>
